      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLEET FLYER (3) well bred four-year-old mare by Zoustar out of Group winning mare Serious Speed on debut for the Quinton yard. Finished off okay in her last two trials and expecting a forward showing with the blinkers going on. Respect. WESTERN LANE (6) returned for his second campaign with a battling on-pace fifth over 1100m at Goulburn. Claim helps but not sure where he gets in the run from the outside draw. Place preferred. TITAN OF FURY (2) returns from a six month break with the one trial over 1000m. Gripped on late at his debut in the heavy (10) going with a fighting second over 1250m at Newcastle two-starts back. Has a stack of gear changes and can run into the minor money. NO VERDICT (4) resumed with a fading fifth in the heavy (9) going in a Super Maiden over 1200m at Nowra. Strips fitter and improvement anticipated from the low draw.",
